{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji23.pdf"],"article":{"title":"待敌分散疲备之时发起歼击为宜","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"待敌分散疲惫之时发起歼击为宜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年5月5日）彭、习："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）如无好仗可打，仍以隐蔽待机，待敌分散并更加疲惫之时，发起歼击为适宜。（二）我们已转至旧安定城西北地区。（三）望每日电告敌情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙丁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微午"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给西北野战兵团司令员兼政治委员彭德怀和副政治委员习仲勋的电报。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":5,"day":5}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":40,"page_end":40},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}